          "class": "DepictionMarkdownView",
          "markdown": "# VisibleIsland\n\n## Dynamic Island for Older Devices\n\nVisibleIsland brings a new and simple way to enable and configure the Dynamic Island on older devices.\n\n## Features\n\n- Enable/disable the Dynamic Island with the flip of a switch\n- Fix the position of the Dynamic Island to be under the notch\n- Set custom X and Y offsets for positioning\n- Hide the Dynamic Island when not in use\n- Fix notification banners position\n- Customize scale and transparency\n- Customize the color of the Dynamic Island\n\n## Compatibility\n\n- iOS 16.0 - 16.6.1\n- Rootless or Roothide (bootstrap + serotonin)\n\n## Supported Devices\n\n- iPhone X, XS, 11 Pro, 13, 13 Pro, 14 (full support)\n- iPhone XR, 11, XS Max, 11 Pro Max, 13 Mini, 13 Pro Max (partial support)",
